{
  "stem": "10272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He signed-- to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where do I go? he said, go ask over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I ask the man at the outside desk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, tomorrow morning, this-and-this hour, you report at the station and this-and-this place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There will be many over there like you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A train will take you home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next day I came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like he said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There  was a lot of Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One would go to all over-- in our area, different places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were all from my-- from my province, this Podkarpatska Rus-- 'Karpatska Rus,' they call it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I'm waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A train comes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This Gestapo puts out-- put us in a train, in a-- not in a cattle train, a normal train, a passenger train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very nice-- we are going with this train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there is one-- one Gestapo was, was going with the-- with the-- with the whole group together with us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we reached the border of Czechia and Slovakia, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia, there was one country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then when Hitler occupied Brno and the whole Czech area, he gave for Slovakia to have their own independent country.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the, the-- there was a Nazi leadership who, who were in contact with the-- with the German-- with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and since they promised to back up the Hitler's policies and everything, carry out anti-Jewish policies and this, they give us, the Slovaks, to have their own-- their own government, their own state.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this Tiso was-- he was a-- was a priest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was named the, the minister or president of that country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Hlinka was his-- the head of the Nazi party in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They called it the Hlinka Guard-- Hlinka Guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
